<div id="pf4430" class="pf w58 h2fe" data-page-no="4430"><div class="pc pc4430 w58 h2fe"><div class="t m536 x0 h5 y2ee5 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">LESSON 1 July 1-7 </div><div class="t mb7 xc4 h174 y2aa7 ff1 fs46 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The Present </div><div class="t mdff xc4 h174 y2392 ff1 fs46 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Condition of the </div><div class="t m417 xc4 h174 y3e8 ff1 fs46 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Church </div><div class="t mec3 x27 h5 y3ff ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;We are all as an unclean thing, and </div><div class="t m5c3 xb9 h5 y386 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">all our righteousnesses are as filthy </div><div class="t m5f2 xb9 h5 yaa ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">rags&quot; (Isa. 64:6). </div><div class="t ma3c x27 h35 y349 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">We may consider ourselves very </div><div class="t m2e1 xb9 h35 ya5d ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">favored and fortunate to have in the </div><div class="t m810 xb9 h35 y1f3 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Word of God a clear message of Christ </div><div class="t m7cc xb9 h35 y331 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">directly addressed to the church. In </div><div class="t m3cf xb9 h35 ycc7 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">eight short verses (Rev. 3:14-21) we </div><div class="t m619 xb9 h35 y493 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">find a description of our spiritual </div><div class="t mf40 xb9 h35 y152 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">condition and of our deep needs. In </div><div class="t m297 xb9 h35 y263 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">these verses our Saviour graciously </div><div class="t mb73 xb9 h35 y9ce ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">offers the remedies to solve our </div><div class="t m23e xb9 h35 y2de ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">spiritual problems. Through Jesus we </div><div class="t m4b6 xb9 h35 ycf6 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">can acquire what we need to pass </div><div class="t m7b6 xb9 h35 ydd ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">through the last and worst crisis of </div><div class="t m8c9 xb9 h35 y1d7 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">history, to meet our Lord, and to </div><div class="t m820 xb9 h35 yc ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">inherit His eternal kingdom of </div><div class="t m98e xb9 h35 y4e7 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">happiness and glory. </div><div class="t m81f x27 h35 y451 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">But we should remember that &quot;the </div><div class="t m5e0 xb9 h35 y17f ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">testimony of the True Witness has not </div><div class="t ma99 xb9 h35 y8a7 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">been half heeded. The solemn </div><div class="t m6c7 xb9 h35 y94 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">testimony upon which the destiny of </div><div class="t m1c4 xb9 h35 yfc5 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the church hangs has been lightly </div><div class="t mb96 xb9 h35 y21b ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">esteemed, if not entirely </div><div class="t mac7 xb9 h35 ya59 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">disregarded.&quot;—Early </div><div class="t m5f7 x30 h35 y6e4 ff5 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Writings, </div><div class="t m16d x43 h35 yac6 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">p. 270. </div><div class="t m5a7 x27 h35 y477 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Further, the way in which each of us </div><div class="t m2db xb9 h35 y2a9 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">either accepts or rejects the message </div><div class="t m4e2 xb9 h35 y711 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">will be a main factor in the shaking </div><div class="t m1b7 xb9 h35 y454 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">movement through which the whole </div><div class="t m2c4 xb9 h35 y26 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">church—and every one of us </div><div class="t m977 xb9 h35 y37f ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">individually—will pass. Whether we  </div><div class="t m78a x58 h35 y87a ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">remain in the church loyal to God, as </div><div class="t m7ba x58 h35 y386 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">whole grain, or whether we are sifted </div><div class="t m1a9 x58 h35 y280 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">away as chaff, depends to a great </div><div class="t ma6d x58 h35 ya39 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">extent upon our response to the </div><div class="t ma78 x58 h35 y3ed ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">message to Laodicea. </div><div class="t mab x21 h35 ya5d ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The </div><div class="t m2165 x9 h35 ya5d ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">-</div><div class="t m745 xa5 h35 y174 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">blessing written by John in </div><div class="t m4b3 x58 h35 y580 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Revelation 1:3 is for those who both </div><div class="t m20e x58 h35 ybc6 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">hear and keep the message of the </div><div class="t ma81 x58 h35 ycc7 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">book of Revelation. Part of the book is </div><div class="t me9 x58 h35 y1b8 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the message to Laodicea. If Revelation </div><div class="t m594 x58 h35 y152 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">is to be a blessing to us, we must </div><div class="t m33a x58 h35 yebb ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;hear&quot; and &quot;keep&quot; the message for </div><div class="t m5ab x58 h35 y3f1 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Laodicea that we shall study this week </div><div class="t m3a9 x58 h35 y100 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">and the next. </div><div class="t m558 x58 h5 ydd ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">DAILY HIGHLIGHTS </div><div class="t m23f x58 h5 y1d7 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">1. </div><div class="t me29 x7 h5 y1d6 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">A Message of Love </div><div class="t m82e x7 h5 yd33 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Rev. 3:14, 15) </div><div class="t m558 x58 h5 y2be ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">2. </div><div class="t m267 x7 h5 y2be ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Lukewarmness </div><div class="t m82e x7 h5 y41a ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Rev. 3:15, 16) </div><div class="t mb7 x58 h5 y17f ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">3. </div><div class="t m1cb x7 h5 y15a ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Insipid Christians </div><div class="t mad2 x7 h5 y6aa ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Rev. 3:16) </div><div class="t m1ce x58 h5 y66 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">4. </div><div class="t m1f4 x7 h5 y94 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Spiritual Self-satisfaction </div><div class="t m4c4 x7 h5 y1a5 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Rev. 3:17-19) </div><div c